data.description: POPULAR AIR BNB COMMUNITY! Spacious 6 Bedroom, 2 bath Raised Ranch. New Metal Roof w/transferrable warranty, New Water Heater & Well Pump, new PVC plumbing. Peaceful setting with Landscaping and Paved driveway! Walking Distance to Community Indoor Pool.  Some renovations have been made; A Mini Makeover should complete the rest. Main bathroom is completely updated and modern with large soaking tub/tiled shower and floors & Custom rustic shelving. 3 Bedroom on upper level and Lower level has 3 additional bedrooms, bath/laundry, large family room that leads out to lower deck. Oversized storage shed! Being Sold AS IS. Tax records listed as 3 Bedroom/1 Bath
